6
00:01:10,470 --> 00:01:25,943
Never a thought of the rumbling
presses that produced them. Completely oblivious to the
vast transportation system that placed them so conveniently
on 14 thousand, strategically located news stands through out the city.

7
00:01:27,470 --> 00:01:31,853
No reason to contemplate what
life without newspapers would mean.

8
00:01:32,690 --> 00:01:36,453
Until it suddenly, and with
little warning, STRIKE!

9
00:01:37,870 --> 00:01:41,070
1700 delivery men ceased work.

10
